ğŸš€ Project Overview

Organizations often have sales data but lack trusted insights into profitability, growth trends, and regional performance.
This project simulates a real-world analytics engineering workflow where raw data is transformed into a clean, reliable analytics layer that supports:

Executive decision-making

BI reporting

