ğŸ¯ Business Problem

The business faced the following challenges:

Sales data existed in raw Excel/CSV format

No clear visibility into:

Profit vs revenue

Product-level margins

Regional performance

Inconsistent and unvalidated data made reporting unreliable

Key questions stakeholders could not answer:

Which products are most profitable?

Which regions drive long-term revenue?

How is revenue trending over time?

ğŸ§© Solution

Designed and implemented a SQL-based analytics engineering system that:

Ingests raw sales data

Applies data quality checks and validation

Transforms raw data into business-ready metrics

Exposes executive-level analytical views

Produces ML-ready time-series features

